Author: throwawayedfeelz
Text: MY JEANS ARE ALL EXACTLY THE SAME? Even the ones way too big for me the zipper. Never. Stays. Fully. UP. I've resorted now to the lifehack of putting that little metal part of a keyring through the zipper and hooking it over the button before buttoning my jeans, and that's the only thing that stops it, jeans are whack
